@NODE "Bugs"

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Bugs
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    * If the sound-subtask pointing to the main-program "hangs" or doesnt exit,
      the sound-subtask can hang and never be exited. I will add a timeout for
      this in a future version.

    * Incompatible cd-roms.
      If you think you own one of theese drives that WarpSDL doesnt seem to
      work with, please drop me a mail describing the model and brand, and
      also what device you are using together with your cd-rom drive.

    Read my lips: "Report the bugs!". :)

@ENDNODE

